Problem :Whenever user wants to shift to new branches or new work stash can help us to save local branch work
Usage :
git stash save "any_name" - from here code will be stored inside your Git repositoryâ€™s .git directory, under the stash list

In order to apply changes git stash apply (if only one stash)  or git stash apply "saved_name"

We are allowed to see stash list using git stash list
